Health and Independence Report 2022 Supplementary Data Tables

Introduction

These supplementary data tables present a range of health data used to inform the 2022 Health and Independence Report and the Pae Ora Health Strategies. These tables present unpublished data sources from within Manatū Hauora and Te Whatu Ora. Additional published data sources used by the 2022 Health and Independence Report and the Pae Ora Health Strategies are referenced in the documents.

This human-readable format can be used to explore the data. Alongside this document, the data is available as a machine-readable CSV file.

Published: July 2023
